383
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:24,717
- [doorbell rings]
- [pounding]

384
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:27,314
[monitor beeps]

385
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:33,190
- [pounding]
- [man] Mr. Foster?

386
00:29:33,280 --> 00:29:34,839
It's the police.

387
00:29:39,840 --> 00:29:40,840
Good morning, officers.

388
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:42,995
