Jeez, you look like hell.

450
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:58,992
[coughing]

451
00:32:59,120 --> 00:33:01,430
Can I get you anything?
Maybe something herbal?

452
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:02,874
