453
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:05,479
Pneumonia.

454
00:33:05,481 --> 00:33:06,960
What a trouper!

455
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:13,109
Ah, you're here.

456
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:15,393
I need you to review the data links

457
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:17,915
