to have favorites, but...

475
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:44,671
Well, I hope that clears everything up.

476
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:45,840
Mm-hmm.

477
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:48,670
- Happy holidays.
- Happy holidays.

478
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:57,959
