627
00:47:24,320 --> 00:47:25,674
[electronic hum, monitor beeps]

628
00:47:26,320 --> 00:47:27,720
[hum, monitor beeps]

629
00:47:29,040 --> 00:47:30,474
Her mind is a blank slate.

630
00:47:30,560 --> 00:47:31,835
Comatose.

