watershed consciousness.

647
00:48:12,960 --> 00:48:14,280
Oh, shit, yeah.

648
00:48:14,360 --> 00:48:16,317
It's like transplant rejection.

649
00:48:17,240 --> 00:48:19,118
We just have to trick the synthetic mind

650
00:48:19,200 --> 00:48:23,752
